  :latex
  "\\label{def:subrepresentation}\nA subspace $W \\subseteq V$ is a \\textit{subrepresentation} (or $G$-invariant\nsubspace) if $\\rho(g)(W) \\subseteq W$ for all $g \\in G$.\nThis notion relies on the setup of \\ref{def:representation}.",
  :type :definition,
