  :latex
  "\\label{rem:conj-classes}\nOver $\\mathbb{C}$, the number of (isomorphism classes of) irreducible\nrepresentations of $G$ equals the number of conjugacy classes of $G$.\nThis follows from \\ref{thm:maschke} and \\ref{thm:schur}.",
