  "\\label{cor:dimension}\nFor a finite group $G$ over $\\mathbb{C}$, combining \\ref{thm:maschke} and\n\\ref{rem:conj-classes},\n\\[\n  \\sum_{\\chi \\in \\hat{G}} (\\dim V_\\chi)^2 = |G|.\n\\]",
